CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Eastside Distilling Inc is a producer and marketer of craft spirits. Its alcoholic beverage categories include whiskey, vodka, gin, rum, tequila, and Ready-to-Drink. Some of its brands include Azunia Tequila, Hue-Hue Coffee Rum, Portland Potato Vodka, and Burnside Whiskey. It operates in a single segment of packaging, producing, marketing, and distributing alcoholic beverages. The company distributes its products in more than 45 states of the United States.
